OL,3,C'It was for my girls': Woman settles
OL,4,Csex discrimination case for #215k
OL,6,FA woman who fought a major financial
OL,7,Finstitution over alleged sex
OL,8,Fdiscrimination has said her motivation
OL,9,Fwas her "two little girls".
OL,11,FMaeve Bradley settled her case against
OL,12,FCitibank N.A. UK for #215,000 after
OL,13,Fbeing supported by the Equality
OL,14,FCommission for Northern Ireland.
