OL,6,FMrs Bradley worked for Citibank in
OL,7,FBelfast as an assistant vice president.
OL,9,FIn the spring of 2023, she went on
OL,10,Fmaternity leave and believed she was
OL,11,Fin line for a promotion on her return.
OL,13,FAhead of her return, Mrs Bradley
OL,14,Fcontacted a manager to let them know
OL,15,Fshe had applied for reduced hours due
OL,16,Fto childcare needs.
