OL,6,FMrs Bradley said she was offered an
OL,7,Falternative role but was not
OL,8,Fcomfortable with this suggestion as
OL,9,Fshe had no experience of the new
OL,10,Fposition.
OL,12,FShe said she asked if anybody on the
OL,13,Fteam had been promoted and was told
OL,14,Fthat the person covering her maternity
